
A comstom component that support a addable attribute and a onAdd event,
to let user handle it directly.



Screenshot
http://screencast.com/t/ld0XK6cGKN

Video for demo 
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uygUAQBQN4M

sample code
<zk>

	<vlayout>
		<tabbox>
			<fiddletabs>
				<tab label="Test" />
				<tab label="Test" />
			</fiddletabs>
			<tabpanels>
				<tabpanel>1</tabpanel>
				<tabpanel>2</tabpanel>
			</tabpanels>
		</tabbox>

		<tabbox>
			<fiddletabs addable="true" onAdd='alert("test")'>
				<tab label="Test" />
				<tab label="Test" />
			</fiddletabs>
			<tabpanels>
				<tabpanel>1</tabpanel>
				<tabpanel>2</tabpanel>
			</tabpanels>
		</tabbox>
	</vlayout>
</zk>